  "bodyText": "CORE\n\nFREE, PRIVATE CYCLE TRACKING\n\nopen-cycle\n\nTrack period dates, flow, symptoms, moods, and notes without making an account. Your entries stay on this device.\n\nWant reminders or exports?\n\nKeep using open-cycle for free everyday tracking. For a larger feature set, Local Cycle offers one-time paid tools like reminders, exports, and richer pattern views.\n\nSee Local Cycle features\nYour privacy\n\nopen-cycle saves your entries on this device. There is no account, no ads, and no required cloud sync for tracking.\n\nThis is a personal wellness log, not medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Talk with a qualified clinician about health concerns.\n\nPrivacy policy\nView source\nLicense terms\nYour cycle log\nDate\nFlow\nNone\nSpotting\nLight\nMedium\nHeavy\nSymptoms\nMood\nNotes\nSave entry\nTotal entries: 1\nLatest entry: 6/27/2026\nClear all entries\n\nEntry saved.\n\nRecent cycle entries\nMedium\n\n6/27/2026\n\nEdit flow\nDelete",
  "rootHtmlSample": "<html lang=\"en\"><head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>open-cycle</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"open-cycle is a simple local-only cycle tracking app inspired by the open-cycle experience.\">\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"./logo.svg\">\n    <script type=\"module\" crossorigin=\"\" src=\"./assets/index-Bk5B0NSX.js\"></script>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" crossorigin=\"\" href=\"./assets/index-CHzNtzez.css\">\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div id=\"root\"><main class=\"page\"><div class=\"container\"><header class=\"hero\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" width=\"72\" height=\"72\" viewBox=\"0 0 220 220\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"110\" r=\"102\" fill=\"#edf1f7\"></circle><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"110\" r=\"70\" fill=\"#ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"0.92\"></circle><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"110\" r=\"68\" stroke=\"#6d7e96\" stroke-width=\"10\" fill=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"110\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#6d7e96\"></circle><circle cx=\"168\" cy=\"110\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#4f607f\"></circle><circle cx=\"52\" cy=\"110\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#4f607f\"></circle><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"52\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#4f607f\"></circle><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"168\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#4f607f\"></circle><path d=\"M110 110L110 52\" stroke=\"#4f607f\" stroke-width=\"8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M110 110L168 110\" stroke=\"#4f607f\" stroke-width=\"8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M110 110L78 78\" stroke=\"#4f607f\" stroke-width=\"7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M110 110L142 142\" stroke=\"#4f607f\" stroke-width=\"7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"110\" r=\"40\" stroke=\"#9aaec7\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-dasharray=\"6 10\"></circle><path d=\"M64 110L50 110M156 110L170 110M110 64L110 50M110 156L110 170\" stroke=\"#b0bdd1\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><text x=\"110\" y=\"198\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#30405a\" font-size=\"16\" font-family=\"Avenir Next, Avenir, Trebuchet MS, sans-serif\" letter-spacing=\"1.5\" font-weight=\"600\">CORE</text></svg><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Free, private cycle tracking</p><h1>open-cycle</h1><p class=\"subtitle\">Track period dates, flow, symptoms, moods, and notes without making an account. Your entries stay on this device.</p></div></header><section class=\"upgrade card\"><h2>Want reminders or exports?</h2><p>Keep using open-cycle for free everyday tracking. For a larger feature set, Local Cycle offers one-time paid tools like reminders, exports, and richer pattern views.</p><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://local-cycle.com\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">See Local Cycle features</a></section><section class=\"card\"><h2>Your privacy</h2><p>open-cycle saves your entries on this device. There is no account, no ads, and no required cloud sync for tracking.</p><p>This is a personal wellness log, not medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Talk with a qualified clinician about health concerns.</p><div class=\"link-row\" aria-label=\"Privacy, source, and license links\"><a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"https://open-cycle.com/privacy\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Privacy policy</a><a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"https://github.com/kborndorff/open-cycle-source\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">View source</a><a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"https://open-cycle.com/license.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">License terms</a></div></section><section class=\"card\"><h2>Your cycle log</h2><form class=\"grid\"><label>Date<input type=\"date\" required=\"\" value=\"2026-06-27\"></label><label>Flow<select required=\"\"><option>None</option><option>Spotting</option><option>Light</option><option>Medium</option><option>Heavy</option></select></label><label>Symptoms<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Cramps, headache, tender breasts\" value=\"\"></label><label>Mood<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Calm, tired, energized\" value=\"\"></label><label class=\"full\">Notes<textarea rows=\"3\"></textarea></label><button type=\"submit\" class=\"button\">Save entry</button></form><div class=\"summary\"><span>Total entries: 1</span><span>Latest entry: 6/27/2026</span></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"button secondary\">Clear all entries</button></section><p class=\"message success\">Entry saved.</p><section class=\"card\"><h2>Recent cycle entries</h2><ul class=\"list\"><li class=\"entry-item\"><div><strong>Medium</strong><p>6/27/2026</p></div><div class=\"entry-actions\"><button type=\"button\">Edit flow</button><button type=\"button\">Delete</button></div></li></ul></section></div></main></div>\n  \n\n\n</body></html>"
